My .vimrc file - updated as I add new configs

# Herald.vim colorscheme, placed in ~/.vim/colors directory
# http://www.h3rald.com/articles/herald-vim-color-scheme/
#
# if you do not have a ~/.vim/colors/ directory you will need to create one

